1:27:27.291 --> 1:27:29.291
I'm tired of feeling like shit.

1:27:30.541 --> 1:27:31.875
What are you saying?

1:27:33.666 --> 1:27:36.208
You were the most important person to me.

1:27:39.541 --> 1:27:40.375
What?

1:27:41.708 --> 1:27:42.708
I still am.

1:27:45.833 --> 1:27:46.833
<i>I love you.</i>

1:27:59.166 --> 1:28:01.291
Listen to what I'm going to tell you.

1:28:03.333 --> 1:28:04.375
It was my fault.

1:28:06.208 --> 1:28:07.208
