No! Cruz!

1:29:08.125 --> 1:29:10.083
No!

1:29:10.166 --> 1:29:13.750
Mom!

1:29:36.583 --> 1:29:37.708
Captain.

1:29:39.208 --> 1:29:40.250
Is something up?

1:29:41.000 --> 1:29:41.833
Alicia.

1:29:41.916 --> 1:29:44.750
We need to discuss something important.
Can we come in?

1:29:46.000 --> 1:29:47.375
I'd rather we talk here.

1:29:47.875 --> 1:29:50.000
Alicia, let's talk inside. Please.

1:30:41.375 --> 1:30:43.208
This is your niece's gun.

1:30:43.291 --> 1:30:45.125
What do I have to do with it?

1:30:45.208 --> 1:30:46.375
Pipa's not here.

1:30:46.458 --> 1:30:48.500
I'm looking for the boy, her son.

1:30:48.583 --> 1:30:51.041
-What for?
-He shot one of my men.

1:30:51.125 --> 1:30:53.458
It wasn't serious,
but things could get worse.

1:30:54.083 --> 1:30:56.125
Tobías could never do such a thing.

1:30:56.708 --> 1:30:59.458
He was armed
with other boys in the backwoods.

1:30:59.541 --> 1:31:02.166
My men found them
while tracking a fugitive.

1:31:06.500 --> 1:31:07.625
Alicia.

1:31:07.708 --> 1:31:08.625
Will you answer?

1:31:24.958 --> 1:31:28.833
Look, Mellino, I told you
I don't know anything, and I'm alone.

1:31:29.750 --> 1:31:33.083
The signal is still here,
and the horse is outside.

1:31:33.166 --> 1:31:35.625
