1:31:52.875 --> 1:31:53.708
Okay.

1:31:54.333 --> 1:31:55.166
Fine.

1:31:56.208 --> 1:31:57.166
Listen, Alicia.

1:31:57.708 --> 1:32:01.000
You have my word
nothing will happen to Pipa or the kid.

1:32:02.083 --> 1:32:04.083
But this needs to end now.

1:32:04.166 --> 1:32:05.125
You're right.

1:32:14.875 --> 1:32:16.041
Chief?

1:32:19.416 --> 1:32:20.416
Follow her.

1:32:39.875 --> 1:32:42.125
