-Snap out of it.
-No.

1:39:05.416 --> 1:39:06.875
Hey, what's up with you?

1:39:07.833 --> 1:39:09.541
Get Mom. Call an ambulance.

1:39:09.625 --> 1:39:12.625
Mom? An ambulance?
Are you nuts? No one can see you.

1:39:12.708 --> 1:39:14.625
Get the SUV, we'll put him in.

1:39:14.708 --> 1:39:16.208
Don't tell a soul, okay?

1:39:16.708 --> 1:39:18.375
Come on, Cruz! Go!

1:39:18.458 --> 1:39:19.416
Go on.

1:39:25.583 --> 1:39:26.666
