1:44:09.541 --> 1:44:11.625
She must be all messed up.

1:45:10.875 --> 1:45:11.708
Mom.

1:45:13.125 --> 1:45:14.000
Mom.

1:45:16.541 --> 1:45:17.625
They're coming.

1:45:24.416 --> 1:45:25.291
Pelari!

1:45:37.375 --> 1:45:38.375
Go that way.

1:45:42.625 --> 1:45:44.583
