1:47:00.250 --> 1:47:01.291
García.

1:47:40.583 --> 1:47:41.875
The belt gun too.

1:47:50.625 --> 1:47:52.583
It didn't have to come to this.

1:47:53.125 --> 1:47:55.875
You know I am a magnet
for policemen like you.

1:47:58.625 --> 1:48:01.375
You told Paredes
to cover it up with the fire.

1:48:02.583 --> 1:48:04.125
Paredes is useless.

1:48:05.291 --> 1:48:08.083
