and get the video back.

1:48:09.083 --> 1:48:10.916
But why did you help him?

1:48:12.041 --> 1:48:15.708
Why cover for the Carrerases?
You didn't have to get involved.

1:48:15.791 --> 1:48:18.458
I'm tired of cleaning up
after the Carrerases.

1:48:19.416 --> 1:48:22.583
-I didn't have a choice.
-That's not true.

1:48:23.916 --> 1:48:25.416
You didn't have to do it.

1:48:25.500 --> 1:48:26.458
Neither did you.

1:48:27.541 --> 1:48:28.583
Yet here we are.

1:48:29.250 --> 1:48:30.833
I'm protecting my son.

1:48:30.916 --> 1:48:32.291
Well, me too.

1:48:37.166 --> 1:48:38.291
Cruz?

1:48:39.583 --> 1:48:40.875
Give me the damn phone.

1:48:42.833 --> 1:48:43.666
I don't have it.

1:48:49.958 --> 1:48:50.791
