1:48:52.083 --> 1:48:53.500
No, Tobías. Put it down.

1:48:58.916 --> 1:49:00.500
Put the gun down, Tobías.

1:49:05.416 --> 1:49:06.500
Listen to me, boy.

1:49:06.583 --> 1:49:08.083
Give me the phone, okay?

1:49:09.833 --> 1:49:12.583
It's okay, Tobías. Give it to him.

1:49:19.958 --> 1:49:21.208
Forgive me, Mom.

1:49:24.250 --> 1:49:25.375
Okay.

1:50:04.333 --> 1:50:08.916
Do you swear to say the truth about
what you know, saw, heard, or perceived

1:50:09.000 --> 1:50:11.333
in connection to Samanta Sosa's murder?

